#DESCRIPTION
##  Algebra: Graphing logarithmic and exponential functions
##ENDDESCRIPTION


## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Exponential and logarithmic expressions and functions)
## DBsection(Graphs)
## Date(01/26/2010)
